EN: I like to take a walk on the small path on weekends.

ZH: 在小路上行驶速度应该慢一点。
EN: You should drive slower on the small road.

ZH: 这个小村庄有很多风景优美的小路。
EN: This village has many scenic and beautiful small paths.

ZH: 小路上的花草散发着迷人的香气。
EN: The flowers and plants on the small path emit a charming fragrance.

ZH: 他们住在小路尽头的那栋房子里。
EN: They live in the house at the end of the small road.

ZH: 我们可以经过小路迂回到目的地。
EN: We can take a detour to our destination through the small path.

